{"tid":2422492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"河南一個村100多人姓罵 有人叫\"罵建行\"銀行拒錄用","createTime":"2021-02-25T08:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T09:31:30.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"eef44b9533cf8ad6e5a79068035ba186ecddf4d4","tid":2422492,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:30:49.000Z","msg":"從小到大總能遇到一些稀有的姓氏<br />\n<br />\n比如這位叫&ldquo;支付寶&rdquo;的大爺<br />\n<br />\n▼<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2Ffdb9cf8bj00qp0nz9000bc000bf0085c.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252Ffdb9cf8bj00qp0nz9000bc000bf0085c.jpg%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=df8d2a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n河南一個村100多人姓罵 有人叫罵建行銀行拒錄用<br />\n<br />\n自我介紹時有點害羞的&ldquo;敢二二&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n▼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被誤以為姓&ldquo;&pi;（pai）&rdquo;的&ldquo;兀（wu）女士&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n▼<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2F6b391ed9j00qp0nza000rc000ty00hyc.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252F6b391ed9j00qp0nza000rc000ty00hyc.jpg%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=1fa98da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2F5683bc8bj00qp0nza001wc000u000gwc.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252F5683bc8bj00qp0nza001wc000u000gwc.jpg%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=63fdc236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在周口商水的一個村莊裡<br />\n<br />\n住著許多姓&ldquo;罵&rdquo;的人家<br />\n<br />\n對，你沒看錯<br />\n<br />\n就是&ldquo;罵人&rdquo;的&ldquo;罵&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2F08fae0bdj00qp0nza0028c000u000gwc.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252F08fae0bdj00qp0nza0028c000u000gwc.jpg%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=f791167a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者一進村子<br />\n<br />\n看見村民罵建舉就懵了<br />\n<br />\n在&ldquo;罵大哥&rdquo;還是&ldquo;罵叔叔&rdquo;的稱呼中猶豫不決<br />\n<br />\n老罵倒是爽快<br />\n<br />\n說自己一般被人稱作&ldquo;罵師傅&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n別看這姓少見<br />\n<br />\n在這村子裡&ldquo;罵&rdquo;姓可是個大姓<br />\n<br />\n大大小小足有一百多口人<br />\n<br />\n記者還見到了<br />\n<br />\n兩個漂亮的罵姓小姐姐<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2F6f7d3ec6j00qp0nza001xc000u000gwc.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252F6f7d3ec6j00qp0nza001xc000u000gwc.jpg%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=b793ae78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稀有的姓氏<br />\n<br />\n讓罵家人自豪的同時<br />\n<br />\n也帶來了不少麻煩<br />\n<br />\n一位阿姨向記者吐槽<br />\n<br />\n她兒子到銀行去應聘<br />\n<br />\n身體都檢查過了<br />\n<br />\n卻在入職前夕被人發現名叫&ldquo;罵建行&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這結局真是讓人心疼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;有趣的姓氏萬裡挑一&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n河南作為中國姓氏的重要發源地<br />\n<br />\n現居住著許多稀有姓氏的後人<br />\n<br />\n比如焦作雪莊村<br />\n<br />\n就住著幾百戶&ldquo;耍&rdquo;家人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n72歲的耍大爺<br />\n<br />\n還因名叫&ldquo;耍螃蟹&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n上了一波熱搜<br />\n<br />\n不少網友評論說：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;這名字聽著就很快樂~&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2Ff661f35fj00qp0nza001tc000u000gwc.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252Ff661f35fj00qp0nza001tc000u000gwc.jpg%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=a6a6fa49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除河南外<br />\n<br />\n全國各地的稀有姓氏<br />\n<br />\n也在漸漸得到人們的關注<br />\n<br />\n陝西魏洛村<br />\n<br />\n有4000多人姓&ldquo;第五&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2Fcdf627baj00qp0nza0012c000u000gwc.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252Fcdf627baj00qp0nza0012c000u000gwc.jpg%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d1c736c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南攸縣菜坪村<br />\n<br />\n有800多人姓&ldquo;叫&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2F92c7e039j00qp0nza0018c000u000gwc.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252F92c7e039j00qp0nza0018c000u000gwc.jpg%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d6ce158a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣西東興一村<br />\n<br />\n有幾千人姓&ldquo;雞&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n村裡的姑娘說<br />\n<br />\n因為姓氏稀奇<br />\n<br />\n從小她就經常被老師點名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在知乎<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;擁有稀有的姓是種怎樣的體驗？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n的問題下<br />\n<br />\n有三萬多條回答<br />\n<br />\n從各種有趣的姓氏背後<br />\n<br />\n不難發現一個問題<br />\n<br />\n很多人都曾因為姓氏&ldquo;奇怪&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n而遭到周圍人的嘲笑和質疑<br />\n<br />\n雖然沒有惡意<br />\n<br />\n但讓當事人聽起來十分難受<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2F4a3e13bbj00qp0nzb002ec000u000gwc.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252F4a3e13bbj00qp0nzb002ec000u000gwc.jpg%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=a5c2af0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另據梨視頻，河南一村莊百余人姓罵，女老師拒絕讓學生稱呼&ldquo;罵老師&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n在河南周口商水縣鄧城鎮周莊村，有13個姓氏分布，但唯獨&ldquo;罵&rdquo;姓格外引人注意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n河南商水一村莊百余人姓罵（來源：視頻綜合）<br />\n        <br />\n周莊村罵姓最長者73歲的罵金停說，罵姓周莊村目前還有21戶，大概180口人。在村子東頭的自家祖墳裡，雖然沒有碑文記載，但是根據長者的墳墓可以推測最早罵姓在清朝雍正年間就存在，罵氏已有百年歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n40歲的罵見鋒說《中國姓氏學發凡》載：原為「馬」姓的一支，清代雍正年間有人在朝中做大官，後反了錯誤，被皇帝下令讓改姓「罵」，世代淪為賤民。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0224%2Fc9e9d2f4p00qp0o1p0098c000u000gum.png&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0224%252Fc9e9d2f4p00qp0o1p0098c000u000gum.png%26thumbnail%3D660x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=049b892d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直到民國初年，添上立人旁成為「傌」姓，表示重新獲得人權。<br />\n<br />\n有人覺得&ldquo;罵&rdquo;姓很不體面不好聽直接改成&ldquo;馬&rdquo;姓，也有人的認為&ldquo;罵&rdquo;姓就像一個燈泡，到哪兒都能發光；有人因為&ldquo;罵&rdquo;姓很快被人記住而覺得驕傲。<br />\n<br />\n罵見鋒認為這個姓的好處就在於，能讓別人很快記得住自己，有時候身邊的人也會開玩笑說，給孩子起名&ldquo;罵得好&rdquo;&ldquo;罵的妙&rdquo;等。雖然這個姓會產生很多尷尬，但這是老祖宗傳下來的，也就坦然接受。朋友一般稱呼其為稱呼&ldquo;老罵&rdquo;&ldquo;小罵&rdquo;或&ldquo;罵哥&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n24歲的罵瓊珊是一名教師，她說因為這個姓，經常遇到尷尬的事情。身為教師的她，學生經常會問罵瓊珊是否稱呼其為&ldquo;罵老師&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人會給她起外號&ldquo;小罵&rdquo;，聽到之後還是很難受的，自己追問自己為什麼不能有個像&ldquo;周&rdquo;&ldquo;王&rdquo;這樣平常的姓氏。罵瓊珊介紹道小時候會介意這個姓，長大後就釋然了，姓氏只是一個代號。"},{"pid":"f2396614c438821eff608bd7d4e604c68b28ae37","tid":2422492,"uid":3241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"駡近平果位係咪比人誅左10族"},{"pid":"88e5ef168bd4c73f641b611decf054eea322f07e","tid":2422492,"uid":5475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"罵近平"},{"pid":"95dbd89c1ebaf0a6d50e7f82ccafec2d5e67444d","tid":2422492,"uid":227588,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"駡中央 vs 駡近平、邊嗰大罪啲？"},{"pid":"e8693dd90463f372ae2ae7bf371fabdf3d8946f3","tid":2422492,"uid":301050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:38:56.000Z","msg":"但係睇嚟個名柒係唔關個姓事"},{"pid":"a1b985b8c7d0ea2787817b8ef59cbedc06ff5a2f","tid":2422492,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:48:59.000Z","msg":"我記得見過話中國有人姓死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6435e5607a159d6365b7db6df05656a841c58b","tid":2422492,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:52:14.000Z","msg":"屠嬌嬌"},{"pid":"f44ddcea67d67d4e555df4a448d225c45a8601b1","tid":2422492,"uid":275114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc6435e5607a159d6365b7db6df05656a841c58b","tid":2422492,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:52:14.000Z","msg":"屠嬌嬌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:55:23.000Z","msg":"白開心"},{"pid":"10e45b610d7bb230d49134a82f3621001f54ae64","tid":2422492,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95dbd89c1ebaf0a6d50e7f82ccafec2d5e67444d","tid":2422492,"uid":227588,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"駡中央 vs 駡近平、邊嗰大罪啲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"而家一定係近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1779779b0229881214944446cf6fb2edbd807cb7","tid":2422492,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"以前識過一個緬甸華僑<br />\n個名叫寸得妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祖籍雲南"},{"pid":"b1bfc69826f6b62a6b40eda286c136112ba44d1a","tid":2422492,"uid":55868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10e45b610d7bb230d49134a82f3621001f54ae64","tid":2422492,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95dbd89c1ebaf0a6d50e7f82ccafec2d5e67444d","tid":2422492,"uid":227588,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"駡中央 vs 駡近平、邊嗰大罪啲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"而家一定係近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"傻啦， 邊會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cadf67b735a63816f8346e5cbcf2f9cde0b0a94","tid":2422492,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:17:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">全撚部都唔係我國人<br />\n我理得佢姓屌娶左李老母<br />\n關我乜事？</span>"},{"pid":"45f594d69398883c6adb693feaf29ae9a5f3c782","tid":2422492,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:19:25.000Z","msg":"令計劃"},{"pid":"73e4f61c1b188cd5438b187db63a57dc6ca3846d","tid":2422492,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cadf67b735a63816f8346e5cbcf2f9cde0b0a94","tid":2422492,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:17:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">全撚部都唔係我國人<br />\n我理得佢姓屌娶左李老母<br />\n關我乜事？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"幽默"}]}